com.google.android.exoplayer2.extractor.mp4

Class AtomParsers

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer2.extractor.mp4.AtomParsers

  • final class AtomParsers
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility methods for parsing MP4 format atom payloads according to ISO 14496-12.

    • Method Detail

      • parseTrak

        public static Track parseTrak(Atom.ContainerAtom trak,
                              Atom.LeafAtom mvhd,
                              long duration,
                              DrmInitData drmInitData,
                              boolean ignoreEditLists,
                              boolean isQuickTime)
                       throws ParserException
        Parses a trak atom (defined in 14496-12).
        Parameters:
        trak - Atom to decode.
        mvhd - Movie header atom, used to get the timescale.
        duration - The duration in units of the timescale declared in the mvhd atom, or C.TIME_UNSET if the duration should be parsed from the tkhd atom.
        drmInitData - DrmInitData to be included in the format.
        ignoreEditLists - Whether to ignore any edit lists in the trak box.
        isQuickTime - True for QuickTime media. False otherwise.
        Returns:
        A Track instance, or null if the track's type isn't supported.
        Throws:
        ParserException

      • parseStbl

        public static TrackSampleTable parseStbl(Track track,
                                         Atom.ContainerAtom stblAtom,
                                         GaplessInfoHolder gaplessInfoHolder)
                                  throws ParserException
        Parses an stbl atom (defined in 14496-12).
        Parameters:
        track - Track to which this sample table corresponds.
        stblAtom - stbl (sample table) atom to decode.
        gaplessInfoHolder - Holder to populate with gapless playback information.
        Returns:
        Sample table described by the stbl atom.
        Throws:
        ParserException - If the resulting sample sequence does not contain a sync sample.

        private static android.util.Pair<java.lang.Long,java.lang.String> parseMdhd(ParsableByteArray mdhd)
        Parses an mdhd atom (defined in 14496-12).

        Parses a stsd atom (defined in 14496-12).
